definitions.definition: Greater than the speed of sound (in the same medium , and at the same temperature and pressure ).
Ultrasonic , having a frequency too high to be audible .

main_definition: ( of a speed ) Greater than the speed of sound (in the same medium , and at the same temperature and pressure ).
secondary_definitions: ( colloquial , of a sound ) Ultrasonic , having a frequency too high to be audible .
